Package info.pavie.opennetworkmap.model.draw.network

This package contains RepresentableNetwork implementations.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Canvas
    A canvas is an editable table where you can insert Network vertices.
    FlexibleGrid<E extends Spatializable>
    A flexible grid is a two-dimensions list where you can store objects.
    Layer
    A layer is a spatialized grid (see FlexibleGrid) which contains Vertex objects.
